  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Accepted)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been reviewed; the assessment team concluded that collectively the evidence supports acceptance. Full structured level data are recorded for 12 of 13 factors; the remaining factor (Model Form) was evaluated through a qualitative expert review process and is documented accordingly.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/cou2-vad-hemolysis-accepted",
